{"tid":1590802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"百萬求一路！香港攰喇，未來可以點樣行落去？宜家需要一個方案，大家一齊幫幫手！","createTime":"2019-09-24T01:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T06:01:15.000Z","uid":296083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6a1abf27ff2b9c6b2ea081d68d8c6c34f9e0a1cb","tid":1590802,"uid":296083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:55:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ideasforHK/photos/a.110642357003196/109897100411055/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FideasforHK%2Fphotos%2Fa.110642357003196%2F109897100411055%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=3041f850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ideasforHK/photos/a.110642357003196/109897100411055/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1百萬想解決7百萬人既問題</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"878c37ce4bbd59de56e05e1a2ef81961d0e8cbed","tid":1590802,"uid":280058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:00:44.000Z","msg":"文筆好巴打可以打返篇中共式打J文<br />\n之後收錢買gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b062412216e173db4d46aba7271186461f96c862","tid":1590802,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=e60ce3f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外就係<br />\n過去個兩個月正正常常係比應屆DSE同學仔溫書休息既<br />\n可惜呢個政府搞到大家奉獻左成個暑假，為左自己又好，為左將來又好，為左下一代又好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前有見連登上有多個關於網上問功課谷既需求，有見及此就有呢個DSE支援服務。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，免費網上問功課谷一直以唔張揚嘅方法存在。谷內有十多位Tutors (當中包括現職老師及名校畢業生在讀生)同DSE同學仔。形式係以分科細谷你問我答為主，亦有提供簡單練習同改文服務。同學亦可以問升學選科等問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直隱姓埋名係為左保障學生安全。但見到需求增加，又多左好多不同既補習post。所以我地希望提供俾同學多一個安全安心既選擇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如有同學有需要，請聯絡：<br />\nTG: mama612<br />\n(暫時有足夠Tutor所以暫不接受更多tutor)<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705916e011b1a5205a058993549eb069d688dfb1","tid":1590802,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def5c48c30ecf2e09b7da2a49f51f7f78000fb70","tid":1590802,"uid":296083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:10:25.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"bc8cc2b153bad9caa1c281135888616f04d555d7","tid":1590802,"uid":296083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:01:15.000Z","msg":"PUSH"}]}